{"tid":1322550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙田衝突】謝振中：警方很早已與商場緊密聯繫","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:01:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"47b3359749a8d995a006d14b8076a56a4733445b","tid":1322550,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1563238113_kT-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1563238113_kT-1280w.jpg&h=c20d5ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在周日沙田反對修訂《逃犯條例》遊行後，警員進入新城市廣場內清場，與示威者發生嚴重衝突，當時商場內亦有為數不少消費的市民。警察公共關係科總警司謝振中在一個電台節目中表示，周日沙田區的遊行途經很多附近商場和街道，警方很早時已與商場有緊密聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n對於事前是否已通知商場，警員會入內拘捕違法人士，謝振中說，平日的拘捕行動，很多時候未必能同時逐一通知，但相關商場是知道警方周日在附近一帶的安保及警方給予的建議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【沙田衝突】不滿警進駐新城市清場-市民一度包圍詢問處促新地交代-180697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E9%A7%90%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E8%A9%A2%E5%95%8F%E8%99%95%E4%BF%83%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3-180697&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4f8caf63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【沙田衝突】不滿警進駐新城市清場-市民一度包圍詢問處促新地交代-180697</a>"},{"pid":"9ce1509abced96beb384ca2e7f43edd9caed1398","tid":1322550,"uid":220701,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"即係打籠通啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"1155e3f10c9d9064d09d90829c3ef0e25f9948eb","tid":1322550,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e80358d2b282c9f01d58ba00ffc43a51f40b9d","tid":1322550,"uid":52032,"like":0,"dislike":